          <li><a href="/dca-calculator/">DCA Calculator</a> — Simulate dollar-cost averaging as an alternative to both HODLing and active trading.</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="hub-backlink"><a href="/calculators/profit-loss/">← All Profit & Loss calculators</a></p>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

